{"tid":1556211,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(fced) 羅范椒芬：有女子向勇士提供免費性愛","createTime":"2019-09-09T15:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:38:00.000Z","uid":75759,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a6391bf6105505a06330a4af257bfee077bada5b","tid":1556211,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bp5XZDY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBp5XZDY.png&h=1bd6220c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登689:姑息沒有底線</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n明報報道：「網上流傳一段影片，片中女士撕走貼在天橋上的反修例宣傳品，並與人以粗言對罵。元朗天主教中學昨發聲明回應有關社交媒體就該校陳副校長的報道，表示會嚴厲處理及跟進事件。教育局表示已收到相關投訴，會按既定程序跟進。<br />\n<br />\n有關網片中，一名女士在學校附近天橋正撕走反修例的宣傳品，拍片者以粗言罵她，她亦以粗言回應「你係咪要&times;啊，除褲喇」。有網民指該女士為元朗天主教中學副校長陳秀芬，質疑她行為不當，稱會向有關機構投訴。」<br />\n<br />\n這是教育學生嗎！？說要學生「除褲屌佢」，大家要問：撕紙狗是誰？該屌的又是誰？這樣姑息隨街提供免費性愛的副校，有一天嘗苦果的是校長和學生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3oxrS9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3oxrS9z.png&h=bf3e0860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E70GySobRdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE70GySobRdA&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=b31972a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E70GySobRdA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">羅范椒芬：有女子向勇士提供免費性愛</span></strong><br />\n羅范椒芬在港台英文節目中，稱自己已經確認（I think we have confirmed that this is a true case），有年輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女子被誤導為「勇士」提供免費性愛，她未有進一步提出實質證據。<br />\n<br />\n羅范椒芬稱，出於私隱原因不能透露任何細節，建議女生須保持警惕，與在示威活動中認識到的「新」朋友聚會時，遠離酒精和大麻，保護自己，免被侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n炒曬車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來單嘢係真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n睇完新聞啦<br />\n我連登689強烈要求連登仔繼續幫手做<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB恥與為伍每日任務</span></span></strong>，唔好次次過兩日就唔記得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要記住TVB係最大支線，係全港最大藍絲產生器呀</span></strong></span>！俾啲耐力，唔好早洩得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼做到10月TVB 簽commitment先可以要TVB陷家剷呀，中途放棄=前功盡廢<br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日任務】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2.洗版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3.罷買<br />\n<br />\n是晚精選@9/9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />潔霸 💎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KaoGroupHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKaoGroupHongKong%2F&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=0de5c70c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KaoGroupHongKong/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去派嬲再留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n枉樓豬一路都用潔霸嘅洗衣產品，點知原來係變相資敵，俾錢佢攞去落廣告養肥TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢嘅洗衣液可以防蟎殺箘，唔知可唔可以洗白返自己品牌落TVB廣告差劣形象呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家唔好再買潔霸任何產品啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更